CONTROLS AND INDICATORS Embraer Legacy 450/500 and Praetor 500/600 Audio Control Panel Pro Line Fusion® Avionics

HDPH Headphone Volume Control

The HDPH knob controls headphone volume. Volume of aural voice and tone warnings to the headphones cannot be adjusted by this knob.
